    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/121cc1fb88dc4a294fff1185dae620b6.poster.avif?t=1770990164\" width=800 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/121cc1fb88dc4a294fff1185dae620b6.webm?t=1770990164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/121cc1fb88dc4a294fff1185dae620b6.mp4?t=1770990164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Match Tree》是一款策略三消游戏，你的每个操作都将引发连锁反应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合小精灵、小矮人与女巫种下的植物。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让灌木成长为大树，让树木化作房屋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规则简单易懂，关卡短小精悍，每一轮都会提升你的解谜技巧。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的智谋足以应对各个关卡的挑战吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/f8e8de965a9e1df031359f94ef5dd829.poster.avif?t=1770990164\" width=800 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/f8e8de965a9e1df031359f94ef5dd829.webm?t=1770990164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/f8e8de965a9e1df031359f94ef5dd829.mp4?t=1770990164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色们为你种下待合成和升级的植物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/66e841b566a7b55f069ea2f7a81a7ae0.poster.avif?t=1770990164\" width=800 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/66e841b566a7b55f069ea2f7a81a7ae0.webm?t=1770990164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/66e841b566a7b55f069ea2f7a81a7ae0.mp4?t=1770990164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >六边形地块允许多元化的组合策略。由你决定参与合成的植物数量与合成体的生长方位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/d8463b6bce0302d66087da9e70aa1b74.poster.avif?t=1770990164\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/d8463b6bce0302d66087da9e70aa1b74.webm?t=1770990164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/d8463b6bce0302d66087da9e70aa1b74.mp4?t=1770990164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当角色被围住时，布局权在你手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/400b6c32f157067997dc01b5c3d2fc40.poster.avif?t=1770990164\" width=800 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/400b6c32f157067997dc01b5c3d2fc40.webm?t=1770990164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/400b6c32f157067997dc01b5c3d2fc40.mp4?t=1770990164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用魔杖等工具破解棘手局面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/da09cff56509d5d6749913a7179f31e1.poster.avif?t=1770990164\" width=800 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/da09cff56509d5d6749913a7179f31e1.webm?t=1770990164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/da09cff56509d5d6749913a7179f31e1.mp4?t=1770990164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但千万要小心那群饿疯了的绵羊！</p>",
